Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:06.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,No way. Me, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.91,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}I wonder if you understand it now,\Nthe thing called the "difference in our skill levels."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:15.21,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}You're the strongest?\NThe Flame Colonel is way stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.75,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs26}He must've had a pretty easy life up until now, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:19.75,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.32,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Oh, you still want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.62,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Come on, brother. It's uncool.\NPicking on the weak like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.62,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,W-Weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:30.36,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:40.80,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Don't think you've won yet!\NI'll settle the score! Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.11,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,That's a perfectly classic cliché line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:46.14,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, my memory’s been terrible lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.01,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.45,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,See you again, you shitty little runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:50.91,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\move(256,438,700,438)\i1}See you again, you shitty little runt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:53.05,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Shitty little runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:57.86,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}Who are you calling a shitty little runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.76,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Oh crap.
